  "title": "Rich Creamy Greek Lamb Skewers",
  "description": "A flavorful Greek dish featuring lamb skewers with a creamy sauce, sake, and ferment-kimchi, perfect for a dinner meal, and is onion and garlic free.",
  "cuisine": "Greek",
