  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the grill to medium high heat.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together sake, lemon juice, olive oil, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Add the lamb pieces to the bowl and marinate for at least 30 minutes.",
    "Thread the marinated lamb onto skewers.",
    "Grill the lamb skewers for 8-10 minutes, turning occasionally.",
    "In a small bowl, mix together yogurt and chopped ferment-kimchi.",
    "Serve the grilled lamb skewers with the creamy yogurt sauce and garnish with chopped parsley."
